      "id": "optimistic_8_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "Fun, honest driver with classic style and plenty of appeal at a sensible price. This car presents respectably and is the kind you can enjoy as-is, but it does show age, wear, and the kinds of cosmetic and detail flaws you\u2019d expect from a fair-condition example. A great fit for someone who wants a usable classic without paying top-tier money.",
