    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_7_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "A classic with real vintage character, this one is best suited for someone looking for a serious project or a parts car with potential. It has the kind of old-school appeal enthusiasts appreciate, but it does need substantial work and is not presented as a ready-to-drive example. If you\u2019ve been searching for an affordable entry point into a restoration, this could be a worthwhile candidate for the right buyer.",
