      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "Older car in fair overall condition with visible age and wear throughout, but still a usable driver for someone looking for an affordable entry point. Expect cosmetic blemishes, an older interior with signs of use, and the kind of imperfections that come with a car that has been driven and not fully restored. It presents decently from a distance but is not a show car, and buyers should plan on some ongoing maintenance and sorting depending on how particular they are. A straightforward, honest candidate for someone who wants a driver-quality example rather than a mint collector car.",
      "price": 17900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Affordable, honest transportation with solid value for the right buyer. This vehicle is best suited for someone seeking a low-cost option, a project, or dependable basic mobility without a big upfront investment. Priced to reflect its condition while still offering real usefulness, it\u2019s a practical chance to get into a vehicle at a very accessible price point.",
      "price": 4950.0,
